item.title: Exploring San Francisco!
item.description: Exploring San Francisco! I’m very excited about this 5-minute video about my favorite city to explore “San Francisco”! This video was filmed around 2019 Christmas over a few biking day trips covering ~50 miles. I hope you are just as excited as I am for this video and thanks for watching! Gear: GoPro Hero 7 (1080p) Music: Dan Skinner, Adam Skinner, Paul Mottram, Philip Sheppard

item.title: Golden Gate Bridge
item.description: Must-see views of the bridge You canâ€™t visit San Francisco without visiting the Golden Gate Bridge! I’ve spent long hours walking, biking & driving around to get different angles of the Golden Gate Bridge. Honestly the views are endless!! I’ll share a few must see angles and their map pin in this post. The Golden Gate Overlook This is a great spot to checkout the bridge. It is seldom crowded and ample free/paid parking spots can be found close by.
